
sequenceDiagram
    participant Driver
    participant Pedal
    participant BrakeController
    participant Brake
    participant Wheel

    Note over Driver,Wheel: Braking Flow (Polymorphic Association)
    Driver->>Pedal: use(p_pression)
    Pedal->>BrakeController: execute(p_pression)
    Note over BrakeController,Brake: BrakeController distributes to 4 Brakes
    BrakeController->>Brake: execute(p_force)
    Brake->>Wheel: reduce speed
    Wheel-->>Driver: Car decelerates